      <title>CTF-crypto-XCTF攻防世界-[Decrypt-the-Message]</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/20/ctf-crypto-xctf-gong-fang-shi-jie-decrypt-the-message/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/20/ctf-crypto-xctf-gong-fang-shi-jie-decrypt-the-message/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="0-考点"><a href="#0-考点" class="headerlink" title="0.考点"></a>0.考点</h1><p>诗歌密码</p><h1 id="1-题目信息"><a href="#1-题目信息" class="headerlink" title="1.题目信息"></a>1.题目信息</h1><img src='/picture/0920-1.png' width='80%'><img src='/picture/0920-2.png' width='80%'><center> 一个诗歌和密文txt文件 </center>【密文】:emzcf sebt yuwi ytrr ortl rbon aluo konf ihye cyog rowh prhj feom ihos perp twnb tpak heoc yaui usoa irtd tnlu ntke onds goym hmpq <h1 id="2-诗歌密码"><a href="#2-诗歌密码" class="headerlink" title="2.诗歌密码"></a>2.诗歌密码</h1><p>诗歌密码的显著特点就是“诗歌”+“密文”。</p><p>下面简要讲解加密步骤</p><h2 id="2-1从诗歌中提取关键字作为密钥"><a href="#2-1从诗歌中提取关键字作为密钥" class="headerlink" title="2.1从诗歌中提取关键字作为密钥"></a>2.1从诗歌中提取关键字作为密钥</h2><p>for my purpose holds to sail beyond the sunset, and the baths of all the western stars until I die.</p><p>从中选择五个词作为关键字：比如“ for”，“ sail”，“ all”，“ stars”，“ die”。</p><p>将它们串在一起，然后给字母编号，编号的规则为:</p><p>以“ a”开头为1，第二个“ a”开头为2，依此类推；如果没有第二个“ a”，则“ b”的编号为2；或者 如果没有“ b”，则“ c”被标记为2，依此类推，直到为所有字母编号。</p><img src='/picture/0920-3.png' width='80%'><center> 密钥编码 </center><h2 id="2-2-用密钥加密明文"><a href="#2-2-用密钥加密明文" class="headerlink" title="2.2 用密钥加密明文"></a>2.2 用密钥加密明文</h2><p>【明文】:We have run out of cigars, situation desperate.<br>因为密钥长度为18，所以我们18个一组排列明文，如下:</p><img src='/picture/0920-4.png' width='80%'><center> 用密钥加密明文 </center><p>生成密文的时候按照密钥的顺序输出， f o r s …</p><p>eudtdkoekcpmwrt…</p><h2 id="2-3-传递密钥"><a href="#2-3-传递密钥" class="headerlink" title="2.3 传递密钥"></a>2.3 传递密钥</h2><p>密钥传递即告知接收方我们选择了哪些词作为密钥，在这里分别是第1个，第6个，第14个，第17个和第20个词，那么最简单的方法就是用密钥标识这几个字符，因此：“a-1、f-6、n-14、q-17、t-20”，然后将“afnqt”,附加到加密的消息上。然后，接收者可以（大致）遵循加密的逆过程来解密消息。</p><p>关于诗歌密码的更多内容参考<a href="http://www.wmbriggs.com/post/1001/">诗歌密码</a></p><h1 id="3-如何破解诗歌密码"><a href="#3-如何破解诗歌密码" class="headerlink" title="3.如何破解诗歌密码"></a>3.如何破解诗歌密码</h1><h2 id="3-1-破解工具"><a href="#3-1-破解工具" class="headerlink" title="3.1 破解工具"></a>3.1 破解工具</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/abpolym/crypto-tools/tree/master/poemcode/">获取解密诗歌密码的工具戳这里</a></p><p>直接运行脚本的话请用python2，当然也可以自己修改为python3格式的。</p><p>如果系统是macos、且没有安装python2可以用如下的方法安装python2环境:</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">brew <span class="token function">install</span> pyenvpyenv <span class="token function">install</span> 2.7.18<span class="token function">vi</span> ~/.zshrc <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#最后一行添加下面的别名</span><span class="token function">alias</span> python2<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'/usr/local/var/pyenv/versions/2.7.18/bin/python'</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 注意换成你安装的路径</span></code></pre><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">import</span> sys<span class="token keyword">import</span> itertools<span class="token keyword">from</span> os <span class="token keyword">import</span> listdir<span class="token keyword">from</span> os<span class="token punctuation">.</span>path <span class="token keyword">import</span> isfile<span class="token punctuation">,</span> joinabc<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz'</span><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">loadlist</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>infile<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    tlist <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> line <span class="token keyword">in</span> open<span class="token punctuation">(</span>infile<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'r'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">for</span> w <span class="token keyword">in</span> line<span class="token punctuation">.</span>split<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> tlist<span class="token punctuation">.</span>append<span class="token punctuation">(</span>w<span class="token punctuation">.</span>lower<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> tlist<span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">encrypt</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>code<span class="token punctuation">,</span> poem<span class="token punctuation">,</span> msg<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Load all words of the poem into a temporary list</span>    twords <span class="token operator">=</span> loadlist<span class="token punctuation">(</span>poem<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Select only those words specified in the code in a new list</span>    pwords <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">''</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> c <span class="token keyword">in</span> code<span class="token punctuation">:</span> pwords <span class="token operator">+=</span> twords<span class="token punctuation">[</span>c<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>lower<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    plen <span class="token operator">=</span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>pwords<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># We can only support encoding all alphabetical letters, a key length greater len(abc) is not reasonable here</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span> plen <span class="token operator">></span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>abc<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> sys<span class="token punctuation">.</span>exit<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Assign an index for each letter in the key based on the alphabet</span>    pcode <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>None<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">*</span> plen    count <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span>    <span class="token keyword">while</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>count<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>plen<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">for</span> al <span class="token keyword">in</span> abc<span class="token punctuation">:</span>            <span class="token keyword">for</span> pc<span class="token punctuation">,</span> pl <span class="token keyword">in</span> enumerate<span class="token punctuation">(</span>pwords<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>                <span class="token keyword">if</span> al<span class="token operator">!=</span>pl<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token keyword">continue</span>                pcode<span class="token punctuation">[</span>pc<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span>count                count<span class="token operator">+=</span><span class="token number">1</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Load all words of the message into a string</span>    mwords <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">''</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> line <span class="token keyword">in</span> open<span class="token punctuation">(</span>msg<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'r'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">for</span> w <span class="token keyword">in</span> line<span class="token punctuation">.</span>split<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> mwords<span class="token operator">+=</span>w<span class="token punctuation">.</span>lower<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    mlen <span class="token operator">=</span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>mwords<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Split message into chunks of size plen, append random (here alphabet) characters to fill the last chunk, if necessary</span>    cpairs <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>    curlen <span class="token operator">=</span> plen    <span class="token keyword">while</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>curlen<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>mlen<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        cpairs<span class="token punctuation">.</span>append<span class="token punctuation">(</span>mwords<span class="token punctuation">[</span>curlen<span class="token operator">-</span>plen<span class="token punctuation">:</span>curlen<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        curlen<span class="token operator">+=</span>plen    rword <span class="token operator">=</span> mwords<span class="token punctuation">[</span>curlen<span class="token operator">-</span>plen<span class="token punctuation">:</span>curlen<span class="token punctuation">]</span>    rlen <span class="token operator">=</span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>rword<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span> rlen <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> plen<span class="token punctuation">:</span> rword <span class="token operator">+=</span> abc<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>plen<span class="token operator">-</span>rlen<span class="token punctuation">]</span>    cpairs<span class="token punctuation">.</span>append<span class="token punctuation">(</span>rword<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Encrypt the message according to the key</span>    cip <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">''</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> i <span class="token keyword">in</span> code<span class="token punctuation">:</span> cip<span class="token operator">+=</span>abc<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span>    cip<span class="token operator">+=</span><span class="token string">' '</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> i <span class="token keyword">in</span> pcode<span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">for</span> pair <span class="token keyword">in</span> cpairs<span class="token punctuation">:</span>            cip <span class="token operator">+=</span> pair<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span>        cip<span class="token operator">+=</span><span class="token string">' '</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> cip<span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">decrypt</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>poem<span class="token punctuation">,</span> cip<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Load all words of the poem into a temporary list</span>    twords <span class="token operator">=</span> loadlist<span class="token punctuation">(</span>poem<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Load all cipher chunks of the ciphertext into a list</span>    cwords <span class="token operator">=</span> loadlist<span class="token punctuation">(</span>cip<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Get the code rom the first chunk and remove it from the ciphertext list</span>    code <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> i <span class="token keyword">in</span> cwords<span class="token punctuation">.</span>pop<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        code<span class="token punctuation">.</span>append<span class="token punctuation">(</span>abc<span class="token punctuation">.</span>index<span class="token punctuation">(</span>i<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Select only those words specified in the code in a new multi-arrayed list</span>    xwords <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token keyword">for</span> x <span class="token keyword">in</span> range<span class="token punctuation">(</span>len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>code<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> xcount<span class="token punctuation">,</span> c <span class="token keyword">in</span> enumerate<span class="token punctuation">(</span>code<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        tlen <span class="token operator">=</span> c        <span class="token keyword">while</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>c<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>twords<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>            xwords<span class="token punctuation">[</span>xcount<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>append<span class="token punctuation">(</span>twords<span class="token punctuation">[</span>c<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>lower<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            c<span class="token operator">+=</span><span class="token number">26</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Get all possible combinations</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> comb <span class="token keyword">in</span> itertools<span class="token punctuation">.</span>product<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">*</span>xwords<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        pwords <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">''</span>        <span class="token keyword">for</span> c <span class="token keyword">in</span> comb<span class="token punctuation">:</span> pwords<span class="token operator">+=</span>c        plen <span class="token operator">=</span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>pwords<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Rearrange the chunks according to the key</span>        pcode <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>None<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">*</span> plen        count <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span>        <span class="token keyword">while</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>count<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>plen<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>            <span class="token keyword">for</span> al <span class="token keyword">in</span> abc<span class="token punctuation">:</span>                <span class="token keyword">for</span> pc<span class="token punctuation">,</span> pl <span class="token keyword">in</span> enumerate<span class="token punctuation">(</span>pwords<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>                    <span class="token keyword">if</span> al<span class="token operator">!=</span>pl<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token keyword">continue</span>                    pcode<span class="token punctuation">[</span>count<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span>cwords<span class="token punctuation">[</span>pc<span class="token punctuation">]</span>                    count<span class="token operator">+=</span><span class="token number">1</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Decrypt the ciphertext</span>        msg <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">''</span>        wlen <span class="token operator">=</span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>pcode<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">for</span> c <span class="token keyword">in</span> range<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> wlen<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>            <span class="token keyword">for</span> word <span class="token keyword">in</span> pcode<span class="token punctuation">:</span>                msg<span class="token operator">+=</span>word<span class="token punctuation">[</span>c<span class="token punctuation">]</span>        <span class="token keyword">print</span> msg<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># first argument = poem</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># second argument = ciphertxt or msg</span><span class="token keyword">if</span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>sys<span class="token punctuation">.</span>argv<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">!=</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> sys<span class="token punctuation">.</span>exit<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#print encrypt([0, 5, 13, 16, 19], sys.argv[1], sys.argv[2])</span>decrypt<span class="token punctuation">(</span>sys<span class="token punctuation">.</span>argv<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> sys<span class="token punctuation">.</span>argv<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><h2 id="3-2-使用方法"><a href="#3-2-使用方法" class="headerlink" title="3.2 使用方法"></a>3.2 使用方法</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">python2 诗歌密码py2.py poem.txt result.txt</code></pre><ul><li>第一个参数放诗歌文件、第二个参数放密文文件</li><li></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
